                                    oc:blockType "paragraph" ;
                                    oc:contentOrder 1 ;
                                    oc:textContent "For each company featured in the key takeaways or notable deals, generate a logo using a two-tier local pipeline. **Do not use Clearbit** (`logo.clearbit.com`) — it is deprecated and consistently fails. External logo CDNs (Brandfetch, logo.dev, Google Favicons) require API keys or are blocked by network restrictions. Instead, use the following approach:" ] ;
