oc:kn_06fcf281 a oc:AntiPattern,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When generating company logos" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Never use Clearbit (logo.clearbit.com) for company logos — it is deprecated and consistently fails. Do not use external logo CDNs requiring API keys." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Clearbit is deprecated; use simple-icons npm package (offline) or sharp-generated initial-based fallback instead" ;
    oc:severityLevel "HIGH" .

oc:kn_2475722c a oc:AntiPattern,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "Before any funding round queries" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Never skip pre-validation of company identifiers before querying funding tools. Always run get_info_from_identifiers first to check resolution and status (Operating vs Operating Subsidiary)." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Skipping pre-validation causes silent empty results — subsidiaries return zero funding rounds and unresolved names waste API calls" ;
    oc:severityLevel "CRITICAL" .

oc:kn_3190f06c a oc:Constraint,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When calling get_rounds_of_funding_from_identifiers" ;
    oc:directiveContent "The role parameter must be 'company_raising_funds' for deal flow digests. Using 'company_investing_in_round_of_funding' returns empty results silently." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Wrong role parameter is a silent failure mode — no error, just empty data" ;
    oc:severityLevel "CRITICAL" .

oc:kn_3a9bb77e a oc:Constraint,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When processing company universes" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Subsidiaries (status='Operating Subsidiary') have zero independent funding rounds — their capital events are tracked at the parent level. Do not query them for funding; note as context only." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Querying subsidiaries wastes API calls and returns empty results that may be misinterpreted as 'no activity'" ;
    oc:severityLevel "HIGH" .

oc:kn_8e5e17a1 a oc:DesignPrinciple,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When designing the PPTX slide layout" ;
    oc:directiveContent "The slide must follow a monochrome-first design philosophy: black, white, and gray dominate. Color is only permitted for semantic meaning (red for down rounds, green for standout metrics) or company logos. The slide should look correct on a black-and-white printer." ;
    oc:hasRationale "Maintains professional financial briefing aesthetic and ensures readability across all output formats" .

oc:kn_ee2d93c2 a oc:AntiPattern,
        oc:KnowledgeNode ;
    oc:appliesToContext "When querying funding data" ;
    oc:directiveContent "Never use get_funding_summary_from_identifiers as the primary data source. It is less reliable and can return errors or incomplete data even when detailed rounds exist." ;
    oc:hasRationale "The summary tool is faster but unreliable; always use get_rounds_of_funding_from_identifiers as primary and summary only for quick aggregate checks" ;
    oc:severityLevel "HIGH" .

